%BA%BFm/poem-b5HNGelufs_wWYmwEaypfg">Ninh Giang dạ phiếm - 寧江夜泛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%E1%BA%A3nh/author-rNqdNPS8u7Eq1xJT55nc6A">Trần Cảnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-di-ch%E1%BB%A9c-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-NJvolbIcDjypA5I_hCVmCw">Thái tử Trương xá nhân di chức thành nhục đoạn - 太子張舍人遺織成褥段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-Hoan/poem-GTCNrO8KpMy-W-0WeDA4Zg">Thị tử Hoan - 示子懽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%BD-C%C3%A1p/V%C3%A3n-qu%C3%A1-H%E1%BA%A3i-V%C3%A2n-quan/poem-vT83_5cqhToPYUmgXZ47xQ">Vãn quá Hải Vân quan - 晚過海雲關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%BD-C%C3%A1p/author-BcCF1ZxvOmWV0_NgUZWaJw">Trần Quý Cáp</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
